                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-8">
                    The Battle Card has all the information that is required for battles that take place during game play.
                    The information generated on the site should be correct, but see the rule book for actual game play.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </dd>
    <dt>Fleet</dt>
    <dd class="ms-3">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col col-4">
                    <a href="../images/BuilderScreen.png" target="_blank">
                        <img src="../images/BuilderScreen.png" class="img-thumbnail" alt="Fleet Builder Screen">
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-8">
                    This is the collection of ships that are brought into game play. The total cost for the fleet should not exceed 10,000.
                    The budget is not enforced, but a warning will be displayed if you exceed your budget.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </dd>
    <dt>Modifier</dt>
    <dd class="ms-3">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col col-4">
