                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-8">
                    The Modifier cards effect the attributes of the ship that they are applied to. The effects of the cards should be order
                    independent, and it is possible that multiple cards can effect the same attributes of the ship.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </dd>
    <dt>Ship</dt>
    <dd class="ms-3">
        A Ship should have a unique name within your Fleet for reference. When a Ship is referenced that is a specific Ship Type card
